      "review_title": "Easy and Hilarious!",
      "review_description": "I love this game! It’s so easy and appears to be geared towards kids, but the animation is hilarious! I love pulling out weeds and vacuuming leaves from the fur. Petting them on the head is so cute with the floating red hearts. And when they bite you, your fingers swell up and turn red. Don’t spray paint them in the face! The lice running through the fur was revolting. I wish there were more levels!",
