      "score": 5,
      "review_title": "Simple and fun 😁",
      "review_description": "This is one of the first games I tried after purchasing my Meta 3 about a month ago. As someone who loves animals, the cute characters are adorable. (Just try not to spray hair dye in their eyes or it's CHOMP😅) The game is easy to learn and a stress free way to spend some downtime. I have completed the game and I think it's the perfect length as it can get repetitive after a while. I recommend if you want to enjoy some stress free gaming.",
